profile_positions.description:
Be part of the Commercial Excellence team and managing a team of 12 rockstars. Develop and execute strategic and operational business and marketing plans to continuously look for growth opportunities using market trends, competitor analysis, and customer insights. Lead, engage, and develop the international marketing team towards highly skilled consumer-centric professionals. Build strong and preferred brands based on a clear brand positioning and framework

• Maximizing the global Customer Base Value and reach New Potentials to improve corporate revenues with a customer centricity approach
• Responsible for developing a Global B2B & B2C qualification and Demand generation infrastructure and plan a Global strategy that guarantees a constant increase in revenue for WHS and for all the Sonova's brands.
• Responsible to create a 360° customer digital strategy journey to guarantee a constant amount of traffic;
• Leading the strategic creation of B2B and B2C journeys;
• Creator of a global infrastructure that connects all the different platforms to create a single point of view and analysis;
• Responsible for paid and organic Global B2C & B2B qualification and Lead generation for all Sonova's brands;
• Analyze and absorb Group companies marketing dynamics and requirements utilizing; understanding to continuously evolve global B2B and B2C organic and paid marketing strategy;
• Working closely with the Directors of Sales and Marketing, Vice President, CFO, CEO to understand the need and translate them in actionable commercial winning activities;
• Leading a team of 10 excellence digital marketing professionals;
